1725
01:28:44,407 --> 01:28:46,910
If we continue
to work this case,

1726
01:28:46,951 --> 01:28:49,454
we will be able
to bring them to justice.

1727
01:28:49,496 --> 01:28:52,207
I also believe there are
people out there

1728
01:28:52,248 --> 01:28:55,001
who know the details
about what happened.

1729
01:28:55,043 --> 01:28:56,878
That's why continue
to take every lead

1730
01:28:56,920 --> 01:28:59,881
and investigate it
as thoroughly as possible

1731
01:28:59,923 --> 01:29:02,217
in hopes that
one of these leads

