01:29:02,258 --> 01:29:05,261
will eventually
lead us to the killer.

1733
01:29:14,979 --> 01:29:16,690
Hold me up, Daddy.

1734
01:29:16,731 --> 01:29:19,067
Here we go.

1735
01:29:19,109 --> 01:29:21,277
Aw, don't cry.

1736
01:29:21,319 --> 01:29:22,904
Aw.

1737
01:29:22,946 --> 01:29:27,075
Hi baby, hello.

1738
01:29:27,117 --> 01:29:31,079
- This is my daughter
