1742
01:29:46,803 --> 01:29:48,263
My son is happy.

1743
01:29:48,304 --> 01:29:49,973
I want to cry every time
I see my son

1744
01:29:50,015 --> 01:29:51,933
because he is so happy.

1745
01:29:51,975 --> 01:29:54,185
He is in a good place now.

1746
01:29:54,227 --> 01:30:00,567
Makes my heart good
to see him happy.

1747
01:30:01,151 --> 01:30:03,194
So life is okay now.

1748
01:30:09,784 --> 01:30:12,287
- Oh, my gosh.
How are you doing?

1749
01:30:16,750 --> 01:30:17,625
- It's so good
to see you.

1750
01:30:17,667 --> 01:30:19,961
- It's good
to see you, too.

1751
01:30:20,003 --> 01:30:21,504
There was a little bit
of nervousness

1752
01:30:21,546 --> 01:30:24,799
about how she would feel
and I would feel

1753
01:30:24,841 --> 01:30:27,677
after so long a time.

1754
01:30:27,719 --> 01:30:30,805
But when I saw her
it was one of those situations

1755
01:30:30,847 --> 01:30:34,351
where you felt like no time
had passed away at all.

1756
01:30:37,520 --> 01:30:39,564
It's such an honor
to have been a part

1757
01:30:39,606 --> 01:30:43,360
of what happened
and where we are today.

1758
01:30:43,401 --> 01:30:48,031
And I know that
Donna wants to continue

1759
01:30:48,073 --> 01:30:51,368
to look at that
every time a child is saved,

1760
01:30:51,409 --> 01:30:53,495
that that makes
a difference to her.

1761
01:30:53,536 --> 01:30:55,455
And it makes
a difference to me, too.

1762
01:30:59,542 --> 01:31:02,420
- The main reason why I'm doing
this documentary today

1763
01:31:02,462 --> 01:31:04,172
is to kind of
let people know

1764
01:31:04,214 --> 01:31:06,549
what kind of
little girl Amber was.

1765
01:31:06,591 --> 01:31:09,177
She's always helping
other little children

1766
01:31:09,219 --> 01:31:12,180
and, and taking care
of children.

1767
01:31:12,222 --> 01:31:14,474
And she always took care
of her little brother.

1768
01:31:14,516 --> 01:31:17,435
So this is just another way
for her to do that.

1769
01:31:17,477 --> 01:31:19,813
She's still doing
what she loved.

1770
01:31:23,233 --> 01:31:26,695
She was not just a victim.
She was my daughter.

1771
01:31:26,736 --> 01:31:29,948
She was somebody.
